data.description: Welcome home to Foxridge! This home features 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, a 2 car garage with epoxy-coated flooring plus a beautiful patio with an added mudroom/sunroom,  the isolated master includes his/her closets & sinks., the living room features a beautiful fireplace and the guest room is also isolated. Your family and loved ones will enjoy this backyard oasis which also includes an added storage building. This home screams location as its convenience is near just about anything one could need. It is also located in CISD Schools. Don't miss your opportunity to see this beauty.
